@startuml

actor Anonymous
participant "Client Portal" as ClientPortal
participant "Backend API" as Backend
participant "Notification Service" as NotificationService

Anonymous -> ClientPortal: Access Registration Page
ClientPortal -> Anonymous: Show Registration Form

Anonymous -> ClientPortal: Enter Email & Phone
ClientPortal -> Backend: Create Client Account Request
Backend -> Backend: Validate Email/Phone
Backend -> Backend: Create Client Record
Backend -> ClientPortal: 201 Client Created
note right of Backend
  New client registered
  Ready to book appointments
end note
Backend -> NotificationService: Send Welcome Email
NotificationService -> Anonymous: Welcome Email
ClientPortal -> Anonymous: Registration Successful

@enduml
